{"type":"article","id":8043,"title":"[翻车啦！]大马华团征文比赛 脸书评论区全面翻车 不要低估大马华人的创意文采","uid":8235,"topics":[1906,163,2697,2885,17,33],"contents":"董总是管理马来西亚华文独中的社团，最近他们和某个中国的什么文化中心搞了个征文比赛，奖励是去广州的机票。<br>\n<br>\n然后一堆大马华人网民就抖机灵发了一堆反串黑中国，和大中华胶的文章作品，空气顿时充满了快活的气息(〃∀〃)<br>\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1482355335249036&amp;id=202019283282654\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1482355335249036&amp;id=202019283282654</a><br>\n不多说，上图！<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/E3nAO7a.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/E3nAO7a.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/E3nAO7a.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/fMlBUSa.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fMlBUSa.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/fMlBUSa.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/s3MvYZa.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/s3MvYZa.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/s3MvYZa.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/dfEm9mH.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dfEm9mH.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/dfEm9mH.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/roFsHJl.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/roFsHJl.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/roFsHJl.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/P5OnuG7.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/P5OnuG7.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/P5OnuG7.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/oc7H5JJ.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oc7H5JJ.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/oc